{"type": "article", "id": 49923, "title": "雅诗兰黛销售额大涨，以及，Dr.Martens 马丁鞋出了浮世绘款 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为了挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-02-05T03:59:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 47576, "name": "Dr.Martens"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 16156, "name": "Acne Studios"}, {"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 10224, "name": "Roger Vivier"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180205114343GIAMFVHDk83EzwLS.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.vogue.com/article/bruno-frisoni-leaves-roger-vivier\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Roger Vivier 创意总监 Bruno Frisoni 离职 </strong></a>| Roger Vivier 宣布，创意总监 Bruno Frisoni 在入职 16 年后决定离职，2 月 27 日将于巴黎发布的 2018 秋季系列会是 Frisoni 负责的最后一个系列。截止至 12 月 31 日的 2017 财年，Tod’s 集团销售额同比下跌 4.1%，旗下的 Roger Vivier 是唯一一个获得增长的品牌，目前，Tod’s 集团还未宣布 Frisoni 的接任者。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2018/02/02/obituaries/pierre-gode-lvmh-dead.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>LVMH 集团董事会成员 Pierre Godé 逝世，享年 74 岁</strong></a>| Pierre Godé 在 1985 年正式加入 Bernard Arnault 的公司，曾参与 LVMH 集团组建，被誉为集团的灵魂人物之一。2015 年，Pierre Godé 从集团退休。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/sales-gains-keep-coming-for-estee-lauder-cos-11135996/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>雅诗兰黛集团第二财季销售额上涨，净利润大跌</strong></a> | 截止至 12 月 31 日的第二财季，雅诗兰黛集团销售大涨 17％ 至 37.4 亿美元，但受美国税改法案影响，净利润同比大跌 71.2％ 至 1.23 亿美元。按类别来看，护肤品类销售额增长最快，为 20%，化妆品上涨了 16%，香水类上涨了 14%。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>2 月 23 日，<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/549092\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dr.Martens</a> 将发售一个花哨的日本浮世绘系列。 </p><p>该系列共有两种鞋款，售价分别为 28000 和 24000 日元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113948YvdUDSVX7cN8OqPL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113948aqj8ZnE1ikMSJDfx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113948xBAXdG4Y1sHgQ0vt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113946MO4jgmYe7L6TDPqs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.611217\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113947FusoCkDeO3QE6K2I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-02-04/acne-18ss-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Acne Studios </a>发布 2018 春夏系列 campaign，请来了美国女演员、歌手 Juliette Lewis 出镜演绎，Lewis 的大动作 pose 配合复古时髦的着装，拍出了特别的 90 年代电影质感。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113916jRH9d0DJyhVpavn7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113916Lg84nriXemN9shxM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113917Ej5lMKwec9BW3ny2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113917JrwguPRStTn6o8Yf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113917L7dO1T6qGoYVHxEX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113918YfbUQCsnoRhqTkKW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/pre-fall-2018/louis-vuitton\" rel=\"nofollow\">Louis Vuitton </a>发布 2018 早秋系列，这一季花样繁多，有干练的皮衣、华贵的皮草、柔美的纱裙，也少不了夸张的长靴和丑丑的运动鞋。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113848Zu3wSDCIA9Mj1PGT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113849PR2A1BbEpmgcGilJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113849mMxi03vd1I4rzFbW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802051138495Fci6qGXlmzdpSKJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802051138503FwtXKxS5qANgM4H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113850TOdZDxpkJRlFIzGe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802051138506vC1sJLRXW8Eybwn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113850QYBsaHR0iDl3EhJe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113850dEqcVQx6XsFifCzP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802051138517GHXECnquFitj803.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802051138523rtFbnIAvz1qPiw8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802051138520kpNQ3fZCW8YgnuP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113851wnOpg6JfmeN0aQcS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113851grPflQjBF4q2kVdb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113853MDJ2BFIl4e3hQYXW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113858Dbp1jyONiVWGgBxk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113859l4FAam0jxzEePgMq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/raf-simons-eastpak-bags-ss18/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Raf Simons 和 Easypak 合作</a>，推出了以《银翼杀手》为灵感的一系列包包，售价在 187 至 312 美元之间。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802051138278Iv6PcFwHqtn1UB9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802051138184CMOhWgqbfRukrvw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113818wNVCYxbvZikaMqgX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113818iSWuDCeBn6fsJvro.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113817sbaU2nJHON81KC0u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113818Mbqge4QFcoPrhvak.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113819Kj136GW9mUtecT02.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/adidas-skateboarding-helas-anime-collection/#slide-10\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Skateboarding</a> 的第二波联名，找来了法国滑板品牌 Helas 合作，从日本动漫中汲取灵感，有 polo 衫、运动鞋和套装等。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113744Y1yWC8MZFvpR956Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667816\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113735bPH2qSOYp0KjtW7d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667816\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113740zOkehLp1WrnC7oNg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667816\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113739kAYlUFpQ4X7vS5Wf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667816\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113739yvQ2FL6N7TDJBnRC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667816\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180205113740oFQBznWviKsTVyre.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667816\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802051137408NbPJUyamrYI9fc0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：acne studios</p>"}